  [Text] Seoul, 11 Apr (XINHUA) -- Korean President Kim 
Yong-sam said here today: "During my recent visit to China, I 
held talks with President Jiang Zemin and Premier Li Peng; we 
frankly and sincerely exchanged views on further developing 
bilateral relations and on issues of common concern. The talks 
