Zuolin, deputy secretary general of the National CPPCC 
committee; Feng Mingwei, Sun Fuling, Chen Zhongyi, Zhu Zhanyu, 
Chen Dabai, Wang Shuhuan, Lu Songhua, Zhang Lianyun, Wang 
Siquan, Wang Zhitai, and Jin Jin, vice chairmen of the municipal 
CPPCC committee; Li Bokang, adviser to the municipal CPPCC 
