<F P=100> Southeast Asia &amp; Pacific </F>
<H3> <TI>   NPC Official Leads Delegation on Visit to Indonesia </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    NPC Official Leads Delegation on Visit to Indonesia </PHRASE></F></HT>

