  [Text] Beijing, April 19 (XINHUA) -- A Chinese Foreign 
Ministry Spokesman here today expressed regret about the recent 
permission by the Japanese Government to allow the Dalai Lama to 
pass through Japan and carry out illicit political activities 
there. 
  "We oppose the Dalai Lama, by any status, going in for 
political activities in other countries, to disrupt China's 
