<F P=102>   OW2104045794 Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service in Chinese 1649 
GMT 19 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> OW2104045794 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service </F>
<F P=105>  Chinese </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Tashkent, 19 April (XINHUA) -- Premier Li Peng went 
to visit personnel of Chinese embassy in Uzbekistan tonight. 
  Li Peng briefed them on the situation in China and his visit 
to Uzbekistan. He said that his trip was very successful and 
that he had extensively exchanged opinions with President 
Karimov about the relations between the two countries. 
  He expressed his hopes that all comrades at the embassy will 
try to do their work better and make new contributions to the 
development of China-Uzbekistan ties. 

</TEXT>

